      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOLID GROOVE (5) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 4 length second (30.90) over 525m at this track. Likely to feature again. WARATAH STORY (2) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.91) last time in a Maiden at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. Cannot be left out. HE'S ALL TALK (1) form hasn't been great but has the inside draw. Last time finished 6th in a Maiden on May 1 over 460m at Geelong behind Harry Time beaten 9 lengths (27.02). Has ability and can atone. WAVE IN SEA (6) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
